### 表

#### 数组

* `ArrayList`，可变数组
* `ArrayList`，`trimToSize()`可以在不在`add()`元素的情况使用，给数组分配固定当前元素所需的容量

##### 代码实现

```java
package adt;

import java.util.Iterator;
import java.util.NoSuchElementException;
import java.util.Spliterator;
import java.util.function.Consumer;

/**
 * 可变数组
 * Created by Shui on 2018/7/7.
 */
public class MyArrayList<T> implements Iterable<T> {
    //capacity [kə'pæsəti] 容量
    private static final int DEFAULT_CAPACITY = 10;
    private T[] theItems;
    private int theSize;

    public MyArrayList() {
        doClear();
    }

    public void clear() {
        doClear();
    }

    private void doClear() {
        theSize = 0;
        ensureCapacity(DEFAULT_CAPACITY);
    }

    public int size() {
        return theSize;
    }

    public boolean isEmpty() {
        return size() == 0;
    }

    public void trimToSize() {
        ensureCapacity(size());
    }

    public T get(int idx) {
        if (idx < 0 || idx > size() - 1) {
            throw new ArrayIndexOutOfBoundsException();
        }
        return theItems[idx];
    }

    public T set(int idx, T newVal) {
        if (idx < 0 || idx > size() - 1) {
            throw new ArrayIndexOutOfBoundsException();
        }
        T old = theItems[idx];
        theItems[idx] = newVal;
        return old;
    }

    private void ensureCapacity(int newCapacity) {
        if (newCapacity < theSize) {
            return;
        }

        T[] old = theItems;
        theItems = (T[]) new Object[newCapacity];
        for (int i = 0; i < size(); i++) {
            theItems[i] = old[i];
        }
    }

    public boolean add(T x) {
        add(size(), x);
        return true;
    }

    public void add(int idx, T x) {
        if (theItems.length == size()) {
            ensureCapacity(size() * 2 + 1);
        }
        for (int i = theSize; i > idx; i--) {
            theItems[i] = theItems[i - 1];
        }
        theItems[idx] = x;

        theSize++;
    }

    public T remove(int idx) {
        T removeItem = get(idx);
        for (int i = idx; i < size() - 1; i++) {
            theItems[i] = theItems[i + 1];
        }
        theSize--;
        return removeItem;
    }

    @Override
    public Iterator<T> iterator() {
        return new ArrayListIterator();
    }

    @Override
    public void forEach(Consumer<? super T> action) {

    }

    @Override
    public Spliterator<T> spliterator() {
        return null;
    }

    private class ArrayListIterator implements Iterator<T> {
        private int current = 0;

        @Override
        public boolean hasNext() {
            return current < size();
        }

        @Override
        public T next() {
            if (!hasNext()) {
                throw new NoSuchElementException();
            }
            return theItems[current++];
        }

        @Override
        public void remove() {
            MyArrayList.this.remove(--current);
        }

        @Override
        public void forEachRemaining(Consumer<? super T> action) {

        }
    }

}
```

#### 链表

##### 为什么要设置头结点？

要是不是用头结点，删除第一个节点就会变成特殊的，删除了第一个节点之后就必须重新调整链表到第一个节点的链

##### 查找节点的优化

使用双向链表，若index小于1/2表长度，则使用头结点挨个向后查找，反之使用尾节点从后往前查找

##### 表达式求值

```java
package com.example.thinkinjava;

import java.util.HashMap;
import java.util.Stack;

public class MyA {
    public static void main(String[] arg) {
        String s = "3*(7-2*3)+5*(9+2*9-6^3+6*7^3)";
//        String s = "3+1";
        char[] cc = s.toCharArray();
        HashMap<Character, Integer> map = new HashMap<>();
        map.put('(', 0);
        map.put('+', 1);
        map.put('-', 1);
        map.put('*', 2);
        map.put('/', 2);
        map.put('^', 3);

        Stack<Integer> data = new Stack<>();
        Stack<Character> op = new Stack<>();

        for (char c : cc) {
            if (c >= '0' && c <= '9') {
                data.push(c - '0');
            } else if (c == '(') {
                op.push(c);
            } else if (c == ')') {
                while (op.peek() != '(') {
                    calcu(data, op);
                }
                //把'('pop出来
                op.pop();
            } else {
                while (!op.isEmpty() && map.get(op.peek()) >= map.get(c)) {
                    //计算
                    calcu(data, op);
                }
                op.push(c);
            }
        }
        while (!op.isEmpty()) {
            calcu(data, op);
        }
        System.out.println(data.pop());
    }

    /**
     * 数字栈中弹出两个元素，符号栈中弹出一个元素进行运算,计算结果压入到数字栈中去
     *
     * @param data
     * @param op
     */
    private static void calcu(Stack<Integer> data, Stack<Character> op) {
        int data1 = data.pop();
        int data2 = data.pop();
        Character opChar = op.pop();
        switch (opChar) {
            case '+':
                data.push(data2 + data1);
                break;
            case '-':
                data.push(data2 - data1);
                break;
            case '*':
                data.push(data2 * data1);
                break;
            case '/':
                data.push(data2 / data1);
                break;
            case '^':
                data.push((int) Math.pow(data2, data1));
                break;
        }
    }
}
```

##### 顺序队列

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)

![img](data:image/png;base64,)

```java
package adt;

/**
 * Created by Shui on 2018/7/14.
 */
public class SqQueue<T> {
    private final int capacity;//队列容量;
    private T[] data;//存放队列数据
    private int rear;//尾指针
    private int head;//头指针
    private int size;//队列数据大小

    /**
     * 初始化
     *
     * @param capacity
     */
    public SqQueue(int capacity) {
        this.capacity = capacity;
        data = (T[]) new Object[capacity];
        rear = 0;
        head = 0;
        size = 0;
    }

    /**
     * 是否是空队列
     *
     * @return
     */
    public boolean isEmpty() {
        return rear == head;
    }

    /**
     * 是否是满的队列
     *
     * @return
     */
    public boolean isFull() {
        return (rear + 1) % capacity == head;
    }

    /**
     * 入队
     *
     * @param elem
     */
    public void enqueue(T elem) throws Exception {
        if (isFull()) {
            throw new Exception("队列已满，无法入队！");
        } else {
            data[rear % capacity] = elem;
            rear++;
            size++;
        }
    }

    /**
     * 出队
     *
     * @return
     */
    public T dequeue() throws Exception {
        if (isEmpty()) {
            throw new Exception("队列为空，无法出队！");
        } else {
            T result = data[head % capacity];
            size--;
            head++;
            return result;
        }
    }

    /**
     * 获取队列数据大小
     *
     * @return
     */
    public int size() {
        return size;
    }
}
```

**注意两点**

* 为了解决“假溢出”问题，使用循环队列。`data[rear % capacity] = elem`
* 为了区别队列已满和队列为空的判断条件，需要损失一个数组空间。
  * 判断队列为空`real == head`
  * 判断队列已满`real % capcity +1 == head`

##### 链表队列

```java
package adt;

/**
 * Created by Shui on 2018/7/14.
 */
public class DoubleLinkList<T> {
    private Node<T> head;
    private Node<T> rear;
    private int size;

    public DoubleLinkList() {
        head = new Node<>();
        rear = new Node<>();
        head.next = rear;
        head.previous = null;

        rear.previous = head;
        rear.next = null;

        size = 0;
    }

    private int size() {
        return size;
    }

    public void addLast(T elem) {
        Node<T> p = new Node<>();
        p.data = elem;

        rear.previous.next = p;
        p.previous = rear.previous;
        p.next = rear;
        rear.previous = p;

        size++;
    }

    public Node<T> getFirst() {
        return head.next;
    }

    public Node<T> getLast() {
        return rear.previous;
    }

    public T removeFirst() throws Exception {
        if (isEmpty()) {
            throw new Exception("链表为空，无法删除");
        }
        Node<T> p = head.next;
        head.next = p.next;
        p.next.previous = head;
        size--;
        return p.data;
    }

    public boolean isEmpty() {
        return rear == head;
    }

    private static class Node<T> {
        private T data;
        private Node<T> previous;
        private Node<T> next;
    }
}

package adt;


/**
 * Created by Shui on 2018/7/14.
 */
public class LinkQueue<T> extends DoubleLinkList<T> {

    public void enqueue(T elem) {
        addLast(elem);
    }

    public T dequeue() throws Exception {
        return removeFirst();
    }

}
```

## 树

### 树的一些概念

![image-20180714125655026](../img/image-20180714125655026.png)

* 没有儿子的节点称之为树叶
* 深度：对任意节点n~i~，n~i~的深度为从根到n~i~的唯一的路径的长
* 高：从n~i~到一片树叶的最长路径的长

树叶的高度都是0

E：高度2，深度1

F：高度1，深度1

### 二叉树

是一个树，其中每个节点都不能有多于两个的儿子

==二叉树的平均深度为$$O(\sqrt{N})$$，二叉查找树，其深度的平均值为$$O(logN)$$==

#### 实现

```java
class BinaryNode {
    T element;
    BinaryNode left;
    BinaryNode right;
}
```

#### 二叉查找树

二叉查找树中的每个节点X，它的左子树小于X，右子树大于X

##### 重复元素的解决

* 定义左子树小于等于节点，或者右子树大于等于节点，把等于定义进来
* 在定义节点的时候另外有一个变量记录相等的情况
